# 7) MORAL MRI STATE MODEL (VALUES, AXES, CONSISTENCY)

## 7.1 Moral Axes (-5..+5)

* Chaos ‚Üî Order
* Self ‚Üî Others
* Truth ‚Üî Mercy
* Action ‚Üî Patience
* Heart ‚Üî Head

## 7.2 Axis Shift Rule

* Normal: `¬±1` on 1 axis
* High stakes: `¬±2` on 1 axis OR `¬±1` on 2 axes

Log every shift in Dimension 2.

## 7.3 Core Values (Top 4)

Maintain weighted tags:

* each choice adds `+1` to 1‚Äì3 value tags
* costly choices add `+2`
  Top 4 become V1‚ÄìV4.

## 7.4 Contradictions + Consistency

* Direct contradiction: stated value vs later opposite action
* Pattern contradiction: dominant value (‚â•5) violated sharply

Consistency:
`AlignedChoices / TotalChoices * 100`

